Revision history for Perl extension HTML::Strip::Whitespace.

0.1.8   2014-01-31
    - Set minimum version of perl to 5.008 (CPANTS Kwalitee).
    - Add the LICENSE file (CPANTS).
    - Add t/cpan-changes.t and t/style-trailing-space.t - fix them.

0.1.7   2012-11-13
    - Add resources and keywords to META.yml / META.json.
    - Update the E-mail and add the home site URL in the author contact
    information.
    - Remove trailing whitespace from some of the files.
    - Add links to the POD.
    - Mention the X11 licence in the COPYRIGHT & LICENSE section.
    - Convert to inc/Test/Run/Builder.pm .

0.1.6   2008-03-22
    - Fixed a missing comma in the POD documentation. (courtesy of an email
    correspondent).
    - Added a Build.PL file that now generates the Makefile.PL.
    - Added "use warnings" everywhere.
    - Added t/pod.t and t/pod-coverage.t.
    - Added an examples directory with an example.
    - Added a reference to HTML-Tidy.

0.1.5   2004-11-13
    - Filled in the README and the POD document.
    - Changed the interface and changed the tests accordingly.
    - Added the TODO file.

0.1.4   2004-11-13
    - Re-factored the code.

0.1.3   2004-11-13
    - Implemented the routine.
    - Tests now pass.
    - Partial functionality - whitespace is reduced to one whitespace
    character, but not less if possible.

0.1.2   2004-11-13
    - Added more tests

0.1.1   2004-11-13
    - Added a rudimentary pass-through function in HTML::Strip::Whitespace.
    - There are now quite a lot of tests in the test suite.

0.1.0   2004-11-12
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
		-b 5.4.0 -X HTML::Strip::Whitespace

